<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>词 on Even - A super concise theme for Hugo</title><link>https://yuanheng521.github.io/categories/%E8%AF%8D/</link><description>Recent content in 词 on Even - A super concise theme for Hugo</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 08:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://yuanheng521.github.io/categories/%E8%AF%8D/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>望海潮·梦冬夜</title><link>https://yuanheng521.github.io/post/%E6%9C%9B%E6%B5%B7%E6%BD%AE%E6%A2%A6%E5%86%AC%E5%A4%9C/</link><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yuanheng521.github.io/post/%E6%9C%9B%E6%B5%B7%E6%BD%AE%E6%A2%A6%E5%86%AC%E5%A4%9C/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;风寒辉玉，疏林流碎，清溪寂月霜华。斜影彻泉，弥汀蕙芷，沉芳漫醉孤鸦。遥瞰柏松岩，夜亭鹤轻舞，尘起人家。冻尽阳春，静凝光转，雾飞花。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;皑皑澄锃银霞，叹扁舟未与，钓叟相拏。笙啸绝巅，菱歌泛咏，飘零恣意英发。穷眄粼涟纡，极乐天原广，辽夐山匝。莫怨黄粱一瞬，心杳境自嘉。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>青玉案·独思</title><link>https://yuanheng521.github.io/post/%E9%9D%92%E7%8E%89%E6%A1%88%E7%8B%AC%E6%80%9D/</link><pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yuanheng521.github.io/post/%E9%9D%92%E7%8E%89%E6%A1%88%E7%8B%AC%E6%80%9D/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;斜光转影时虚度，岁不淹，归何去？醉梦闲潭痴闲书。孤独妙论，寂寞巧语，戚戚心潮舞。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;​芸芸众里觅几度，劳神烦思愧谈吐。魂悸忽兴雨尽宿，万千巷陌，谁知结于，此人愁衷处。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>菩萨蛮·读飞卿</title><link>https://yuanheng521.github.io/post/%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E8%9B%AE%E8%AF%BB%E9%A3%9E%E5%8D%BF/</link><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://yuanheng521.github.io/post/%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E8%9B%AE%E8%AF%BB%E9%A3%9E%E5%8D%BF/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;娥黛鬟浓波芒艳，言赋韵成意缱绻。舒怀辞堂皇，摛采溢流光。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;枘圜鸷相扞，庭春筠难安。风起拂君袂，漫咏雪絮飞。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>